Class PatchSetViewerFragment

  • java.lang.Object
    • Fragment
      • com.jbirdvegas.mgerrit.fragments.PatchSetViewerFragment

  • public class PatchSetViewerFragment
extends Fragment
    Class handles populating the screen with several cards each giving more information about the patchset

    All cards are located at jbirdvegas.mgerrit.cards.*
